{"tid":7204,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"Red Bull比賽ViuTV女神受傷疑一度失憶 送院嚴重轉穩定！！","createTime":"2016-11-27T17:37:10.000Z","updateTime":"2016-11-28T08:21:25.000Z","uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"61b6e8c7cb3e9eecd81cd127066edbced5374c2c","tid":7204,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-27T17:37:10.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/news/20161127/55973492\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fnews%2F20161127%2F55973492&d=oF%2B7shHiHnXH04nVPe8eUsW%2Flfx08C7TTpsJ%2BRLLqlo%3D&h=be61bc88\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fnews%2F20161127%2F55973492&h=c610de57\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/news/20161127/55973492</a><br />\n於啟德跑道公園舉行的Red Bull Flugtag飛行日，發生多宗意外，5人受傷，送往聯合醫院救治，其中一名傷者是懷疑一度短暫失憶、有ViuTV女神之稱的32D女主持楊偲泳（Renci）。現場消息雖指，楊當時只是受驚過度，正在醫院檢查腦部，惟醫院發言人指，23歲的楊情況嚴重，正在觀察病房治理，至晚上9時半，情況轉為穩定。 <br />\n<br />\n大會強調一向注重比賽安全，現場已安排2名蛙人、4名獨木舟操作人員及5艘救生艇，應付突發情況及水面救援；岸上另設有2個救護站，有醫護人員當值。而所有參賽者出席活動前，均已簽署免責聲明。 <br />\n今年大會挑選了41支參賽隊伍進入決賽，有不少娛樂名人參加，除楊偲泳外，英皇娛樂的歌手鍾舒漫、陳凱彤及許靖韻也有參與。"},{"pid":"eba62c8641bd12d4c7c5c90a9570f9aa780aff2e","tid":7204,"uid":9520,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-27T17:38:32.000Z","msg":"相？"},{"pid":"d635b4dddb2be3fba24bc1b56e1e99f227fa2ee7","tid":7204,"uid":11713,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-27T17:43:15.000Z","msg":"不孝有三 無圖為大"},{"pid":"bc7f6670f3cbaa5ee3139c251e1ea715d526c72f","tid":7204,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-27T20:52:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7c33cab108e2fcc3a7ff1d287d3f47cc1b3a0dc4","tid":7204,"uid":20430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-28T03:04:13.000Z","msg":"神你老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class